data.description: Experience the epitome of comfortable living in this charmingly updated brick home, accentuated by a stunning kitchen! Numerous upgrades adorn this home, including fresh paint, flooring enhancements, updated light fixtures, and ceiling fans. The redesigned extended galley kitchen boasts a breakfast bar, exquisite granite countertops, a coffee bar, gleaming stainless steel appliances, and an abundance of cabinets for all your culinary needs. The open-concept lower level seamlessly connects the spacious living room to the kitchen, promoting a sense of togetherness. A separate dining area adds a cozy touch and offers direct access to the kitchen. The grand foyer entrance welcomes you! The laundry room offers under stair storage as well as direct access to the attached two-car garage. Upstairs, three generously sized bedrooms await, along with two additional well-appointed bathrooms. The primary ensuite pampers you with a granite countertop vanity and a spacious walk-in closet.  Additionally, an expanded landing area can serve as a versatile play space or cater to your various needs. Out back, a fenced backyard beckons, complete with a covered back patio and an extended deck, providing the perfect setting for all your entertainment needs. This outdoor haven is an ideal spot for pets and children to frolic and play. The home also boasts a welcoming covered front porch, complemented by easy-to-maintain front yard landscaping and a comforting shade tree. Check this beauty out today!
